<td class="navbox-abovebelow" style=";" colspan="2"><span class="noprint plainlinks navbar" style=""><span style="">This box:</span> <span style="white-space:nowrap;word-spacing:-.12em;"><a href="/wiki/Template:Scots_language" title="Template:Scots language"><span style="" title="View this template">view</span></a> <span style=""><b>·</b></span> <a href="/wiki/Template_talk:Scots_language" title="Template talk:Scots language"><span style="" title="Discuss this template">talk</span></a> <span style=""><b>·</b></span> <a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/w/index.php?title=Template:Scots_language&amp;action=edit" class="external text" rel="nofollow"><span style="" title="Edit this template">edit</span></a></span></span></td>
