<h3><span class="editsection">[<a href="/w/index.php?title=Scots_language&amp;action=edit&amp;section=13" title="Edit section: Dictionaries and linguistic information">edit</a>]</span> <span class="mw-headline" id="Dictionaries_and_linguistic_information">Dictionaries and linguistic information</span></h3>
<ul>
<li><a href="http://www.dsl.ac.uk/dsl/" class="external text" rel="nofollow">The Dictionary of the Scots Language</a></li>
<li><a href="http://www.scotsdictionaries.org.uk/" class="external text" rel="nofollow">Scottish Language Dictionaries Ltd.</a></li>
<li><a href="http://www.scots-online.org/grammar/pronunci.htm#cairt" class="external text" rel="nofollow">Dialect Map</a></li>
<li><a href="http://www.scots-online.org/airticles/phonetics.htm" class="external text" rel="nofollow">SAMPA for Scots</a></li>
<li><a href="http://www.stooryduster.co.uk/" class="external text" rel="nofollow">Scottish words – illustrated</a></li>
<li><a href="http://cf.linguistlist.org/cfdocs/new-website/LL-WorkingDirs/pubs/papers/browse-papers-action.cfm?paperid=5007" class="external text" rel="nofollow">Abstract: Vowel height harmony and blocking in Buchan Scots</a>, Mary Paster, <a href="/wiki/University_of_California" title="University of California">University of California</a>, Phonology Vol. 21, Issue 3</li>
<li><a href="http://www.scotsindependent.org/features/scots/index.htm" class="external text" rel="nofollow">Scots Language Recordings</a></li>
</ul>
<h3><span class="editsection">[<a href="/w/index.php?title=Scots_language&amp;action=edit&amp;section=14" title="Edit section: Collections of texts">edit</a>]</span> <span class="mw-headline" id="Collections_of_texts">Collections of texts</span></h3>
